ttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-the-maximum-age-of-humans-115-or-older-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edefinition%20of%20biological%20age%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20how%20to%20measure%20it%3B%20Verdin%20uses%20GlycanAge%20and%20SuPar%2C%20which%20use%20inflammation%20markers%20to%20measure%20aging.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20uses%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Ffitness-wearables-trackers-pros-cons-wellness-experts-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewearable%20tech%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Whoop%20smartwatch%2C%20to%20keep%20tabs%20on%20his%20blood%20pressure%20and%20cholesterol%2C%20and%20makes%20lifestyle%20changes%20accordingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20his%20results%2C%20Verdin%20believes%20that%20diet%20has%20a%20huge%20impact%20on%20longevity.%20He%20follows%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchef-grew-up-mediterranean-diet-tricks-add-fiber-meals-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMediterranean-style%20diet%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20includes%20lots%20of%20fresh%20produce%2C%20legumes%2C%20whole%20grains%2C%20and%20lean%20proteins%2C%20and%20avoids%20ultra-processed%20foods.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20look%20at%20populations%20that%20are%20on%20this%20type%20of%20diet%2C%20they%20really%20are%20the%20healthy%20ones%2C%26quot%3B%20Verdin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22eec55ec9-3af1-48d2-9686-bdc72d48b2b6%5C%22%3EWhy%20a%20sweet%20breakfast%20is%20bad%20for%20longevity%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBreakfast%20should%20be%20savory.%20So%20no%20pastries%2C%20no%20orange%20juice%2C%20no%20fruity%20yogurt%2C%26quot%3B%20Verdin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEating%20a%20sugary%20or%20high-carb%20meal%20on%20an%20empty%20stomach%20can%20cause%20your%20blood%20sugar%20to%20spike%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20it%20does%2C%20it%20sets%20you%20up%20for%20the%20whole%20day%20of%20bouncing%20up%20and%20down%20with%20your%20blood%20sugar%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20means%20you're%20likely%20going%20to%20experience%20energy%20crashes%20and%20cravings%20throughout%20the%20day%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-eat-carbs-without-blood-sugar-spikes-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erise%20in%20blood%20sugar%20after%20eating%20carbs%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20natural%20and%20not%20necessarily%20a%20problem.%20However%2C%20having%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F5-warning-signs-you-might-have-high-blood-sugar-doctors-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echronic%20high%20blood%20sugar%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20increase%20inflammation%20over%20time%2C%20aging%20your%20body%20and%20raising%20your%20risk%20of%20chronic%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2291833ede-342e-426c-90cb-17d11edf435a%5C%22%3EStart%20the%20day%20with%20fiber%2C%20protein%2C%20and%20good%20fats%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EVerdin%20typically%20eats%20eggs%2C%20avocado%2C%20and%20salmon%20(either%20smoked%20or%20cooked)%20with%20wholemeal%20bread%20for%20breakfast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20not%20particularly%20fussed%20about%20how%20his%20eggs%20are%20cooked%2C%20but%20prefers%20to%20use%20olive%20oil%20over%20butter.%20%26quot%3BIf%20one%20prefers%20no%20oil%2C%20hard%20boiled%20would%20be%20the%20best%20method%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEggs%20and%20salmon%20both%20contain%20healthy%20fats%20and%20protein%2C%20which%20help%20you%20feel%20full%20throughout%20the%20day.%20Wholemeal%20bread%20and%20avocado%20add%20fiber%20to%20the%20meal%2C%20which%20is%20important%20for%20digestive%20health%20as%20it%20feeds%20the%20%26quot%3Bgood%26quot%3B%20bacteria%20in%20the%20gut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flongevity-scientist-shared-breakfast-for-avoiding-blood-sugar-spikes-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1