0it%20work%3F%20The%20Chakh%20De%20Chole%20vending%20machine%20is%20designed%20to%20mimic%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F298533%2Fchhatisgrah-bhajjiya-mangodi-stall-owner-innovates-machine-make-pakoras-fritters-fast%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eactions%20of%20a%20street%20vendor%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20with%20precision.%20The%20machine%20dispenses%20exactly%20the%20right%20amount%20of%20chickpeas%20(%3Cem%3Echhole%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20spices%2C%20onions%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Echutney%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20every%20time.%20The%20best%20part%3F%20It%20is%20all%20automated.%20Customers%20can%20choose%20between%20three%20spice%20levels%20by%20pressing%20the%20buttons%2C%20including%20less%20spicy%2C%20medium%20spicy%2C%20or%20spicy.%20The%20machine%20then%20assembles%20the%20perfect%20plate%20within%2060%20seconds.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20exactly%20how%20a%20vendor%20would%20make%20it%20by%20hand%2C%20but%20with%20the%20consistency%20of%20a%20machine%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sagar%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20use%20fresh%20ingredients%20every%20day%2C%20and%20nothing%20is%20stored%20overnight.%20The%20chickpeas%20are%20boiled%20fresh%20in%20our%20kitchen%20every%20morning%2C%20and%20the%20machine%20is%20cleaned%20and%20loaded%20with%20fresh%20ingredients%20every%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekulchas%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20grilled%20manually%2C%20but%20Sagar%20is%20already%20working%20on%20the%20next%20version%20of%20the%20machine%2C%20which%20will%20bake%20them%20too%2C%20making%20the%20entire%20process%20fully%20automated.%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20it%20to%20be%20easy%20and%20convenient%20for%20my