the%20Rajouri%20Garden%20outlet%2C%20%E2%80%9CAt%20first%2C%20I%20was%20a%20bit%20hesitant%20about%20whether%20%3Cem%3Echhole%20kulche%3C%2Fem%3E%20from%20a%20vending%20machine%20could%20capture%20the%20real%20taste%20and%20flavour.%20But%20I%20was%20genuinely%20surprised.%20The%20taste%20was%20spot%20on%2C%20better%20than%20I%20expected.%20I%20have%20already%20been%20to%20the%20outlet%20twice%2C%20and%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20get%20enough%20of%20it.%20The%20spices%20are%20perfectly%20blended%2C%20and%20the%20best%20part%20is%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20ready%20in%20just%2060%20seconds%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20so%20convenient.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20quick%20and%20delicious%20meal%20that%20has%20made%20a%20place%20in%20my%20heart.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20heart%20behind%20Chakh%20De%20Chole%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20banker%20credits%20the%20venture%E2%80%99s%20success%20to%20his%20family.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F406059%2Fsubramani-kho-kho-world-cup-journey-tamil-nadu-sports%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efamily%20has%20been%20incredibly%20supportive%3C%2Fa%3E.%20My%20mother%2C%20especially%2C%20was%20a%20huge%20inspiration%20for%20me.%20When%20I%20told%20her%20I%20wanted%20to%20quit%20banking%20and%20do%20something%20of%20my%20own%2C%20she%20did%20not%20hesitate%20to%20back%20me%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sagar%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%202387px)%20100vw%2C%202387px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2F20250103_162015-2_11zon-1746189545.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222387%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chakh%20De%20Chole%20has%20earned%20a%20revenue%20of%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20so%20far%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2F20250103_162015-2