0documents%20for%20a%20Real%20ID%20before%20the%20May%207%20deadline.%3Cp%3EMichael%20M.%20Santiago%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20women%20who%20have%20changed%20their%20name%20through%20marriage%20or%20divorce%20are%20struggling%20to%20get%20Real%20IDs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESeveral%20women%20told%20BI%20they've%20had%20to%20make%20multiple%20trips%20to%20try%20and%20get%20the%20right%20marriage%20documents.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAmericans%20are%20scrambling%20to%20get%20Real%20IDs%20ahead%20of%20the%20deadline%20to%20get%20the%20identification%20for%20flights.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20last%20summer%2C%20Debra%20Kohn%20became%20very%20well-acquainted%20with%20her%20local%20Pennsylvania%20DMV.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20ended%20up%20making%20three%20trips%20there%2C%20along%20with%20one%20to%20the%20clerk's%20office%2C%20to%20obtain%20a%20valid%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-id-deadline-air-travel-delayed-2025-drivers-license-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReal%20ID%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20all%20because%20her%20marriage%20certificate%20from%201986%20was%20from%20a%20justice%20of%20the%20peace%2C%20not%20the%20county.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarting%20May%207%2C%20anyone%20getting%20on%20a%20domestic%20flight%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20able%20to%20use%20an%20old%20driver's%20license.%20Instead%2C%20they%20will%20need%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-id-deadline-air-travel-delayed-2025-drivers-license-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReal%20ID%20%3C%2Fa%3Eor%20other%20form%20of%20valid%20identification.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20Kohn%2C%20Americans%20need%20to%20bring%20a%20slew%20of%20documents%20to%20the%20DMV%2C%20including%20an%20original%20marriage%20certificate%20for%20those%20who%20have%20changed%20their%20names.%20Getting%20an%20original%20marriage%20certificate%20from%20the%20state%20usually%20takes%20weeks%20and%20costs%20a%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKohn%20isn't%20alone%20in%20her%20Real%20ID%20difficulties.%20Though%20many%20married%20or%20divorced%20women%20have%20the%20necessary%20documents%20handy%20or%20can%20get%20them%20relatively%20easily%2C%20others%20have%20taken%20to%20social%20media%20to%20share%20their%20difficulties.%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20four%20women%20about%20the%20lengthy%2C%20often%20confusing%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20the%20Transportation%20Department%2C%20TSA%2C%20and%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222fe841be-9d27-4e6f-892d-1084fd722dc3%5C%22%3E'Extremely%20frustrating'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKohn%2C%2068%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20she%20probably%20spent%20six%20hours%20getting%20the%20necessary%20certificate%20%E2%80%94%20one%20with%20an%20official%20raised%20seal%20%E2%80%94%20between%20her%20many%20trips%20and%20time%20spent%20at%20the%20DMV.%20She%20hasn't%20heard%20of%20any%20of%20her%20friends%20having%20similar%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJessiqua%2C%20a%2034-year-old%20in%20Oklahoma%20who%20asked%20to%20go%20by%20her%20first%20name%20for%20fear%20of%20retaliation%20from%20her%20ex-husband%2C%20said%20lengthy%20divorce%20proceedings%20made%20it%20difficult%20for%20her%20to%20get%20a%20Real%20ID%20in%202020%20and%202021%2C%20even%20though%20she%20wasn't%20even%20switching%20back%20to%20her%20maiden%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20went%20to%20get%20my%20Real%20ID%2C%20they%20wanted%20my%20marriage%20certificate%20and%20they%20wanted%20my%20divorce%20document%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20divorce.%20I%20didn't%20have%20a%20divorce%20document%2C%20I%20had%20to%20fight%20for%20one.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20she%20got%20a%20legal%20separation%20document%20from%20her%20lawyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJulie%20Anderson%2C%20a%2058-year-old%20in%20Massachusetts%2C%20said%20she%20got%20%26quot%3Blucky%26quot%3B%20when%20applying%20for%20a%20Real%20ID%20in%20April%20of%20this%20year.%20Divorced%20but%20with%20her%20ex-husband's%20last%20name%2C%20she%20only%20brought%20a%20copy%20of%20her%20marriage%20license%20(along%20with%20a%20divorce%20decree).%20The%20DMV%20employee%20talked%20to%20his%20supervisor%20and%2C%20somehow%2C%20they%20accepted%20her%20copy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20person%20at%20the%20desk%20said%2C%20'I'm%20really%20surprised%20they%20did%2C'%26quot%3B%20Anderson%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BLuckily%20they%20did%2C%20because%20I%20went%20to%20my%20files%20and%20I%20went%20through%20everything%2C%20I%20don't%20even%20own%20a%20copy%20of%20my%20original%20marriage%20license.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDiane%20Wagner%2C%2053%2C%20wasn't%20as%20fortunate%20and%20found%20the%20whole%20process%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20frustrating.%26quot%3B%20She%20visited%20her%20DMV%20office%20in%20St.%20Louis%2C%20Missouri%2C%20three%20times%20in%20one%20day%20to%20try%20and%20get%20the%20right%20marriage%20certificate%2C%20because%20the%20copy%20she%20had%20at%20home%20wasn't%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20whole%20day%20running%20around%2C%20between%20waiting%20in%20line%20and%20finding%20all%20my%20items%20and%20going%20back%20and%20waiting%20in%20line%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20she%20paid%20a%20fee%20and%20applied%20for%20a%20certified%20marriage%20certificate%20online%2C%20which%20arrived%20about%20two%20weeks%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHad%20I%20known%20there%20was%20gonna%20be%20all%20these%20hoops%2C%20I%20maybe%20never%20would've%20changed%20my%20name%2C%26quot%3B%20Wagner%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223071b4ad-0fd9-4688-9ec0-57f9bbddef6f%5C%22%3EPeople%20are%20scrambling%20to%20get%20their%20IDs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Real%20ID%20Act%2C%20passed%20in%202005%2C%20was%20a%20response%20to%20the%20S