s%20of%20the%20Sexual%20Harassment%20of%20Women%20at%20Workplace%20(Prevention%2C%20Prohibition%20and%20Redressal)%20Act%2C%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKey%20findings%20from%20both%20studies%20reveal%20a%20startling%20lack%20of%20awareness%20among%20all%20major%20respondents%20regarding%20safe%20workplaces%2C%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20and%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%202013%20Act.%20Compliance%20with%20the%20Act%20was%20found%20to%20be%20minimal%2C%20and%20the%20issue%20of%20safe%20workplaces%20in%20the%20context%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20was%20not%20considered%20a%20fundamental%20aspect%20of%20working%20conditions%20or%20a%20labour%20issue%20for%20women%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-18_11zon-1-1746188348-500x262.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Orientation%20on%20sexual%20harassment%20of%20women%20at%20the%20workplace%20for%20tea%20garden%20workers%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-18_11zon-1-1746188348-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-18_11zon-1-1746188348-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-18_11zon-1-1746188348-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-18_11zon-1-1746188348-150x79.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-18_11zon-1-1746188348.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-424635%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22262%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EOrientation%20on%20sexual%20harassment%20of%20women%20at%20the%20workplace%20for%20tea%20garden%20workers%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20this%20gap%2C%20Sanhita%20adopted%20a%20trauma-informed%2C%20survivor-centred%20approach%20to%20initiate%20the%20first%20intervention%20of%20its%20kind%20in%20these%20sectors.%20Through%20long-term%20community%20engagement%20and%20the%20creation%20of%20safe%2C%20non-judgmental%20spaces%2C%20women%20began%20naming%20their%20experiences%2C%20many%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20These%20conversations%20were%20facilitated%20with%20care%2C%20centring%20healing%2C%20trust%2C%20and%20the%20lived%20realities%20of%20the%20women%20involved.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-17_11zon-1-1746188875.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Consultation%20in%20collaboration%20with%20CII%5Cn%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-17_11zon-1-1746188875.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-17_11zon-1-1746188875-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-17_11zon-1-1746188875-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-17_11zon-1-1746188875-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-17_11zon-1-1746188875-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-424650%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EConsultation%20in%20collaboration%20with%20CII%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20scale%20up%20the%20efforts%2C%20Sanhita%20identified%20grassroots%20women%20leaders%20(called%20champions)%20from%20the%20workers%20group%2C%20who%20are%20now%20mobilising%20others%2C%20building%20awareness%2C%20and%20advocating%20for%20safer%20workplaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlongside%20this%2C%20Sanhita%20works%20with%20trade%20unions%2C%20Employers%E2%80%99%20Associations%20and%20the%20Labour%20Department%20to%20improve%20institutional%20accountability.%C2%A0As%20a%20result%20of%20Sanhita%E2%80%99s%20continuous%20engagement%20with%20trade%20unions%20in%20the%20jute%20industry%2C%20both%20central%20and%20mill-based%2C%20over%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20Sexual%20Harassment%20of%20Women%20at%20Workplace%20related%20demands%20were%20included%20in%20the%20Charter%20of%20Demands%20of%20Jute%20Mill%20Workers%20during%202022%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20history%20of%20trade%20unions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20persistent%20dialogue%20and%20engagement%20with%20various%20stakeholders%2C%20Sanhita%20successfully%20addressed%20systemic%20gender%20discrimination%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20revision%20of%20the%20retirement%20age%20for%20women%20jute%20mill%20workers%20from%2055%20to%2058%20years%2C%20equal%20to%20that%20of%20their%20male%20peers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20despite%20these%20advances%2C%20the%20issue%20remains%20largely%20absent%20from%20funding%20priorities.%20Safe%20workplaces%20in%20the%20informal%20sector%20and%20margins%20of%20the%20formal%20sector%20are%20often%20overlooked%20in%20philanthropic%20agendas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEfforts%20like%20Sanhita%E2%80%99s%20reveal%20the%20urgent%20need%20to%20invest%20in%20community-driven%20strategies%20that%20build%20both%20voice%20and%20systems.%20These%20initiatives%20not%20only%20protect%20women%20workers%20but%20also%20challenge%20the%20structural%20conditions%20that%20have%20kept%20them%20silent%20for%20too%20long.%20Dignity%20and%20safety%20at%20work%20are%20not%20a%20luxury%2C%20they%20are%20rather%20fundamental.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFisherfolk%20of%20Thiruvarur%20district%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%3A%20defending%20traditional%20rights%20and%20livelihoods%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThiruvarur%20district%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20with%20its%2047.2%20km%20coastline%20along%20the%20Palk%20Strait%2C%20is%20home%20to%20the%20traditional%20fishers%20of%20the%20Muthupet%20Lagoon.%20For%20generations%2C%20these%20communities%20have%20depended%20on%20the%20lagoon%E2%80%99s%20resources%2C%20practising%20sustainable%20fishing%20methods%20that%20have%20been%20passed%20down%20through%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20these%20fishers%20have%20faced%20increasing%20challenges%20in%20retaining%20their%20customary%20rights%20over%20the%20lagoon%E2%80%99s%20resources%2C%20including%20access%20to%20fishing%20grounds%20and%20involvement%20in%20resource%20management%20and%20decision-making%20processes.%20While%20environmental%20regulations%2C%20such%20as%20the%20CRZ%202019%2C%20play%20a%20vital%20role%20in%20conservation%2C%20they%20often%20overlook%20the%20knowledge%20and%20needs%20of%20local%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20gap%20has%20led%20to%20economic%20hardship%2C%20depletion%20of%20marine%20resources%20due%20to%20unsustainable%20practices%2C%20and%20the%20erosion%20of%20traditional%20governance%20systems%20that%20have%20historically%20helped%20preserve%20the%20lagoon%E2%80%99s%20ecological%20balance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20situation%20highlights%20the%20need%20for%20policies%20that%20integrate%20both%20environmental%20protection%20and%20the%20livelihoods%20of%20local%20communities.%20By%20combining%20modern%20conservation%20efforts%20with%20the%20indigenous%20knowledge%20that%20has%20long%20contributed%20to%20the%20lagoon%E2%80%99s%20sustainability%2C%20both%20the%20fishers%E2%80%99%20future%20and%20the%20health%20of%20the%20lagoon%20can%20be%20protected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrassroots%20organisations%20like%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%2