-Facebook-Ad-2025-04-30T220922.780_11zon-1746031177.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-04-30T220922.780_11zon-1746031177-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-04-30T220922.780_11zon-1746031177-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-04-30T220922.780_11zon-1746031177-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-04-30T220922.780_11zon-1746031177-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-424419%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShubham%20conducts%20demonstrations%20of%20the%20EV%20Doctor%20for%20dealers%20so%20they%20know%20the%20benefits%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20major%20priority%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20was%20thermal%20runaway%2C%20the%20phenomenon%20where%20a%20battery%20overheats%20and%20potentially%20catches%20fire.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20EV%20Doctor%20team%20had%20done%20extensive%20testing%20in%20this%20area%2C%20which%20allowed%20us%20to%20train%20the%20AI%20models%20with%20real-world%20data.%20It%20gave%20the%20device%20a%20strong%20edge%20over%20other%20solutions%20in%20terms%20of%20risk%20prediction%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20their%20success%2C%20the%20co-founders%20consider%20EV%20Doctor%20just%20the%20beginning.%20Their%20next%20project%2C%20under%20the%20umbrella%20of%20Energy%20AI%20Labs%2C%20is%20to%20build%20a%20universal%20operating%20system%20for%20batteries%2C%20essentially%20giving%20%E2%80%98a%20brain%20to%20every%20battery%20on%20Earth.%E2%80%99%20This%20platform%20will%20allow%20continuous%20diagnostics%2C%20live