at%20struck%20me%20deeply%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20From%20that%20moment%2C%20Ashin%20decided%20to%20move%20away%20from%20imitating%20and%20instead%20focused%20on%20creating%20something%20truly%20original.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20fruit%20of%20this%20new%20mindset%20came%20in%20Class%209%2C%20when%20Ashin%20built%20a%20mini%20smart%20portable%20Android%20projector%20%E2%80%94%20without%20referring%20to%20any%20tutorials%20or%20guides.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20project%20made%20me%20believe%20I%20could%20actually%20innovate%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20The%20young%20innovator%20decided%20then%20that%20everything%20he%20created%20henceforth%20must%20be%20unique%2C%20purposeful%20and%20have%20social%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98The%20biggest%20regret%20of%20my%20life%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20Ashin%20completed%20school%20in%202019%2C%20he%20had%20already%20built%20a%20smart%20portable%20air%20conditioner%20which%20used%20minimal%20energy.%20The%20invention%20earned%20him%20a%20spot%20at%20the%20prestigious%2046th%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20National%20Science%2C%20Mathematics%20and%20Environment%20Exhibition%20(JNNSMEE)%20by%20NCERT%20and%20won%20third%20place%20at%20the%20state%20level.%20Naturally%2C%20expectations%20soared%2C%20and%20he%20was%20urged%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20Indian%20Science%20Congress%20(a%20national%20event%20where%20young%20innovators%20present%20their%20best%20projects)%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20most%20prestigious%20science%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20fate%20had%20other%20plans.%20That%20year%E2%80%99s%20theme%20was%20agriculture%2C%20and%20Ashin%E2%80%99s%20air%20conditioner%20project%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20selected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20just%2017.%20I%20missed%20the%20invitation%20from%20Rashtrapati%20Bhavan%2C%20the%20opportunity%20to%20speak%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20and%20to%20be%20awarded.%20That%20regret%20stayed%20with%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20admits.%20For%20someone%20who%20had%20put%20his%20heart%20into%20innovation%2C%20the%20disqualification%20stung%20deeply.%20But%20it%20also%20planted%20a%20new%20idea%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20would%20soon%20take%20root%20in%20the%20most%20unexpected%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20bathroom%20realisation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%202019%2C%20while%20still%20grappling%20with%20the%20disappointment%2C%20Ashin%20applied%20for%20the%20Nanshan%20Entrepreneur%20Star%20Contest%202019%20by%20the%20Shenzhen%20municipal%20government.%20He%20was%20selected%20as%20a%20semi-finalist%20and%20received%20a%20robot%20TS100%20tank%20chassis%20(a%20compact%2C%20tracked%20robotic%20platform%20often%20used%20for%20building%20mobile%20robots)%20as%20a%20gift.%20Around%20the%20same%20time%2C%20his%20thoughts%20lingered%20on%20agriculture%20%E2%80%94%20the%20theme%20that%20had%20cost%20him%20a%20life-changing%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-30T192030.033-1746021054.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22robot%20TS100%20tank%20chassis%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-3